# Karuna — Frontend Design Specification
> Complete screen-by-screen guide for designers and developers.

---

## 🎨 Global Design System

### Colors
| Token | Usage | Suggested Color |
|-------|-------|----------------|
| `--color-primary` | Buttons, links, accents | Orange `#F97316` |
| `--color-secondary` | Secondary buttons, donate | Blue `#3B82F6` |
| `--color-danger` | Urgent/critical items | Red `#EF4444` |
| `--color-warning` | Moderate items | Amber `#F59E0B` |
| `--color-success` | Stable/fulfilled | Green `#22C55E` |
| `--color-bg` | Page background | Dark `#0F172A` |
| `--color-card` | Card backgrounds | `#1E293B` |
| `--color-text` | Body text | `#F1F5F9` |
| `--color-muted` | Placeholder, labels | `#94A3B8` |

### Typography
- **Font**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Min body size**: 16px (outdoor readability per PRD)
- **Headings**: Bold, high contrast
- **Labels**: All-caps, small, muted

### Rules (from PRD §10)
- All critical actions reachable in **≤ 3 taps**
- **Mobile-first** — design at 375px width first
- **High contrast** — outdoor sunlight readability
- **Emergency chatbot button always visible** in header
- Red/orange/green urgency color coding must be consistent

---

## 📱 Page Index

| Page | Route | Access |
|------|-------|--------|
| Home / Auth | `/` | Public |
| Site Dashboard | `/dashboard` | Authenticated |
| Doctor Site Page | `/site/:id/doctor` | Doctor only |
| Pharmacy Site Page | `/site/:id/pharmacy` | Pharmacy only |
| Nurse Page | `/site/:id/nurse` | Volunteer (NURSE track) |
| Driver Page | `/site/:id/driver` | Volunteer (DRIVER track) |
| Helper Page | `/site/:id/helper` | Volunteer (HELPER track) |
| Donate Hub | `/donate` | Public |
| Monetary Donation | `/donate/monetary` | Public |
| In-Kind Donation | `/donate/inkind` | Public |
| Emergency Chatbot | `/help` (slide-over panel) | Public |

---

## 🏠 Page 1 — Home / Auth `/`

### Header (Persistent across all pages)
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Karuna Logo | SVG/Image | Top-left, links to `/` |
| [Help Me] | Button | Top-right, **orange**, opens `/help` chatbot panel |
| [Donate] | Button | Top-right, **blue**, links to `/donate` |

### Role Selector Tabs
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Doctor Tab | Toggle Button | Default NOT selected |
| Pharmacy Tab | Toggle Button | Default NOT selected |
| Volunteer Tab | Toggle Button | **Default selected** |
> On tab click: form fields below change dynamically — no page reload

---

