| Phone Number | Tel input | ✅ | "+91 XXXXX XXXXX" |
| Date of Birth | Date picker | ✅ | DD/MM/YYYY |
| Blood Group | Dropdown | ✅ | A+, A-, B+, B-, O+, O-, AB+, AB- |
| Profession | Text input | ✅ | "e.g. Nurse, Teacher, Driver" |
