---

### OTP Verification Step (appears after submit)
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Info text | Text | "OTP sent to +91 XXXXX" |
| OTP Code | 6-digit pin input | Auto-focus, number only |
| [Verify OTP] | Button | Orange |
| [Resend OTP] | Text link | Muted, 30s countdown |

**API Calls:**
- `POST /api/auth/register` with all form fields → on first visit
- `POST /api/auth/login` with phone → sends OTP
- `POST /api/auth/verify-otp` with phone + token → returns `access_token`
- Store `access_token` in localStorage / secure cookie

