## 🗺️ Page 2 — Site Dashboard `/dashboard`

> All 3 roles (Doctor, Pharmacy, Volunteer) land here after login.

### Header (same as global)
Add: **User avatar / name** top-right with role badge (Doctor / Pharmacy / Volunteer)

### Site Cards Grid
- **3 columns** desktop → 2 tablet → 1 mobile
- Sorted by urgency (highest first — comes pre-sorted from backend)

**Each Site Card contains:**
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Site Name | Heading (H2) | Bold, white |
| Location | Small text | Muted, with 📍 icon |
| Patient Count | Badge | "👥 42 patients" |
| Urgency Badge | Color badge | Red=Critical, Yellow=Moderate, Green=Covered |
| Personnel Needs | Tags | "Needs: 3 Doctors · 5 Nurses · 2 Drivers" — color coded |
| [Volunteer Here] | CTA Button | Full-width, orange |

> Clicking [Volunteer Here] → calls `POST /api/sites/:id/join` → then routes to role-specific page

**API Calls:**
- `GET /api/sites` → fetch all sites
- `GET /api/sites/:id/stats` → live personnel counts shown on card

---

## 🩺 Page 3 — Doctor Site Page `/site/:id/doctor`

### Top Section
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Site name + back button | Header | "← General Hospital" |
| Patient count | Stat badge | "32 Patients" |

### Patient Tag List
Each patient is a **collapsible card**:

**Collapsed state:**
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Patient ID | "TAG-001", bold |
| Triage badge | Urgent (red) / Moderate (yellow) / Stable (green) |
| Status icons | Pending orders indicator |
| [Expand ▼] | Chevron icon |

**Expanded state — Order Form inside each card:**
| Field | Type | Required | Placeholder |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| Medicines Needed | Text input | ❌ | "e.g. Paracetamol 500mg" |
| Equipment Needed | Text input | ❌ | "e.g. IV drip, Oxygen mask" |
| Quantity | Text input | ✅ | "e.g. 2 strips, 1 unit" |
| Priority | Dropdown | ✅ | Urgent / Medium / Low |
| Notes for Nurse | Textarea | ❌ | "Instructions for nurse..." |
| [Submit Order] | Button | — | Orange |

**Below the form — Existing orders for this patient:**
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Order item row | Medicine name + quantity + priority badge |
| Status tag | Pending (grey) / Available (green) / Unavailable (red) |

**API Calls:**
- `GET /api/patients/:siteId` → list all patient tags
- `POST /api/patients` → create new patient tag (if site admin)
- `PUT /api/patients/:id` → update triage / notes
- `POST /api/orders` → submit order for a patient
- `GET /api/orders/:siteId?status=pending` → view order statuses

---

## 💊 Page 4 — Pharmacy Site Page `/site/:id/pharmacy`

### Top Section
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Site selector | Dropdown | "Supplying: General Hospital" → `GET /api/sites` |
| Back button | Icon button | ← |

### Order Queue
Each order is a card:
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Patient ID | "TAG-003" |
| Medicine / Equipment | Item name |
| Quantity | Requested quantity |
| Priority badge | Urgent (red) / Medium (yellow) / Low (grey) |
| Status Buttons | 3 options below |

**Status action buttons (per order item):**
| Button | Action | Color |
|--------|--------|-------|
| [Available ✓] | Sets status → `available` | Green |
| [Partially Available] | Sets status → `partially_available` | Yellow |
| [Unavailable ✗] | Sets status → `unavailable` | Red |

**When all items are marked, show:**
| Button | Action |
|--------|--------|
| [Order Ready for Pickup 🚚] | Sets all → `ready_for_pickup` |

**API Calls:**
- `GET /api/orders/:siteId` → fetch pending orders
- `PUT /api/orders/:id` with `{ status, pharmacy_notes }` → update each item

---

## 🏥 Page 5 — Nurse Page `/site/:id/nurse`

### Top Section
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Track badge | "You are: 🏥 Nurse Volunteer" |
| Site name | Heading |

### Todo List
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Add task input | Text input | "Add a new task..." |
| [+ Add] | Button | Small, orange, right of input |

**Each todo item:**
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Checkbox | Check to mark complete |
| Task description | Text |
| Patient tag link | Optional "TAG-002" badge |
| Status badge | Pending / In Progress / Completed |
| [Delete] | Small icon button (trash), red |

**API Calls:**
- `GET /api/volunteer-todos/:siteId` → load my todos
- `POST /api/volunteer-todos` → add a task
- `PUT /api/volunteer-todos/:id` → mark complete / in progress
- `DELETE /api/volunteer-todos/:id` → remove

---

## 🚗 Page 6 — Driver Page `/site/:id/driver`

### Top Section
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Track badge | "You are: 🚗 Driver Volunteer" |

### Delivery Task List
Tasks fetched from `GET /api/orders/:siteId/pickup`

**Each task card:**
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Priority badge | Red = Urgent (🔒 mandatory), Yellow = Medium, Green = Low |
| Item description | "Deliver: Paracetamol 500mg x 10 to TAG-003" |
| From (Pharmacy) | Address / name |
| To (Site) | Site name + location |
| [Mark as Delivered] | Button, green |
| 🔒 Locked card style | For urgent/mandatory deliveries — cannot skip |

> **Locked red card** = `mandatory: true` from backend — must be completed first (per Blueprint)

**API Calls:**
- `GET /api/orders/:siteId/pickup` → get pickup queue
- `PUT /api/orders/:id` with `{ status: "delivered" }` → mark done

