### Top Section
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Track badge | "You are: 🤝 Helper Volunteer" |
| Assigned Lead | "Report to: Nurse Sita / Head Chef Ramu" |
| Report Location | "Go to: Zone B, Tent 3" |

### AI-Generated Task List (auto-populated from volunteer assignment)
Same todo UI as Nurse page — pre-filled with `suggested_tasks` from the AI response.

**API Calls:**
