## 💰 Page 9 — Monetary Donation `/donate/monetary`

| Field | Type | Required | Placeholder |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| Donor Name | Text input | ❌ | "Anonymous or your name" |
| Email | Email input | ❌ | "For receipt" |
| Phone | Tel input | ❌ | "For receipt via SMS" |
| Amount | Number input | ✅ | "Enter amount" |
| Quick amounts | Preset buttons | — | ₹100 / ₹500 / ₹1000 / ₹5000 |
| [Proceed to Pay] | Button | — | Blue, full-width |

> Payment gateway (Razorpay/Stripe) integration — button redirects to gateway

**API Calls:**
- `POST /api/donations` with `{ type: "monetary", amount, donor_name, email, phone }`

---

## 📦 Page 10 — In-Kind Donation `/donate/inkind`

| Field | Type | Required | Placeholder |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| Donor Name | Text input | ❌ | "Your name or org name" |
| Phone | Tel input | ❌ | "For coordination" |
| Items Description | Textarea | ✅ | "e.g. 50 blankets, 20 food packets" |
| Delivery Choice | Radio / Toggle | ✅ | See below |

**Delivery Choice (Toggle):**
| Option | Label | Shows next |
|--------|-------|------------|
| I'll deliver myself | 🚗 Self Delivery | Site location details |
| Pick up from me | 📍 Arrange Pickup | Address input |

**If Self-Delivery selected — show:**
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Site list | Cards with site name + address → "Deliver here" |

**If Pickup selected — show:**
| Field | Type | Required | Placeholder |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| Pickup Address | Textarea | ✅ | "Your full address" |
| Info text | Text | Muted | "A driver will contact you for pickup" |

| Button | Details |
|--------|---------|
| [Submit Donation] | Orange, full-width |

**API Calls:**
- `POST /api/donations` with `{ type: "inkind", items, self_delivery: true/false, delivery_address }`
- Response includes AI-generated category + delivery message

---

## 🆘 Page 11 — Emergency Chatbot `/help`
> Opens as a **full-screen slide-over panel** from the [Help Me] button in the header. Always accessible.

### Chat Interface
| Element | Details |
|---------|---------|
| Header | "🆘 Karuna Emergency Assistant" + close X |
| Emergency numbers | Pinned top bar: 📞 112 · 108 · 1078 |
| Chat messages | Bubble layout — user (right, orange) / AI (left, dark) |
| Typing indicator | Animated dots when AI is responding |

### Input Area (bottom)
| Element | Type | Details |
|---------|------|---------|
| Message input | Textarea | "Describe your situation..." |
| [Send] | Icon button | Orange arrow, or Enter key |

> First message should auto-suggest prompts:
> - "I am stuck and need help"
> - "I need medical assistance"
> - "Where is the nearest safe zone?"

**API Calls:**
- `POST /api/chatbot/chat` with `{ message, history: [...previousMessages] }`
- Store history in local state for multi-turn conversation

---

## 🔑 Shared Auth Logic

| Action | When | API Call |
|--------|------|---------|
| Store token | After OTP verify | `localStorage.setItem('token', access_token)` |
| Attach token | Every protected request | `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header |
| Fetch profile | After login | `GET /api/auth/me` → get role, track, site |
| Redirect by role | After login | Doctor → `/dashboard`, Volunteer → `/dashboard` |
| Redirect by track | After joining site | NURSE → `/site/:id/nurse`, DRIVER → driver page, etc. |

---

## 🚨 Global States to Handle

| State | UI Response |
|-------|------------|
| Offline | Banner: "You are offline. Showing cached data." |
| Loading | Skeleton loaders (not spinners) on card grids |
| Empty state | "No sites available right now" with illustration |
| API error | Toast notification — red, bottom of screen |
| Success | Toast notification — green, bottom of screen |
